    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 87.</p><p>Tier II: Sharpened Magic</p><p>Prerequisite: Magical Geometry</p><p>Arcane Damage. Whenever you deal damage with a spell of 5th-level or lower, you can choose to change the damage type of the spell to force damage for the purpose of overcoming resistances.</p><p>Burst of Magic. When you deal damage with a spell, you can choose to deal maximum damage with that spell. Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
